### 2. Deep Analysis & Extraction
Created a comprehensive analysis document [japanese_design_library.md](file:///C:/Users/user/.gemini/antigravity/brain/ac80a7c7-7f1c-4809-87be-ae3348505ba1/japanese_design_library.md) which breaks down:
